      "options": "<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0; border-left: 4px solid #17a2b8;\">\n<h5 style=\"margin-top: 0; color: #0c5460;\">How Approval Routing Works</h5>\n<ol style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 20px;\">\n<li><strong>Account Matching:</strong> System finds approval line matching the expense account</li>\n<li><strong>Default Fallback:</strong> If no match, uses line with \"Apply to All Accounts\"</li>\n<li><strong>Amount Filter:</strong> Each level activates only if amount falls within Min-Max range</li>\n</ol>\n<h5 style=\"color: #0c5460;\">Setup Best Practices</h5>\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 20px;\">\n<li>Create at least one line with <strong>Apply to All Accounts</strong> as fallback</li>\n<li>For specific accounts, create separate lines with dedicated expense accounts</li>\n<li>If no level matches the amount, request will <strong>auto-approve</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</div>"
